#

Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Savory Herb Mashed Potatoes

45 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin coated in a blend of fresh herbs, served alongside creamy mashed potatoes infused with savory flavors.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • dried thyme: 1 tsp
  • dried rosemary: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • potatoes: 2 large
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • milk: 1/4 cup
  • fresh parsley: 2 tbsp
